title: Speedo Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Raw, Western, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Favorite among locals and tourists alike, so is very busy, but worth the wait. Has an ever changing menu selection. Located in the trendy north side of the city. There are raw meals, organic herbal teas, as well as offering clearly labeled vegan items, in addition to gluten and dairy free choices.
